data.description: Don't miss this amazing opportunity to own a piece of prime real estate in Royersford Borough and Spring-Ford School District! This charming twin on North 5th Ave has been lovingly cared-for by the same family for over 50 years. The seller is generously offering a 1 Year Home Warranty from America's Preferred Home Warranty to help ensure a smooth transition as you make this wonderful home your own.  Situated on historic North 5th Ave in the Borough of Royersford, this property is the picture of style and convenience. This property is adjacent to the local park/ playground and walkable to a variety of shopping destinations.  A commuter's dream, your new home is close to major routes and state highways. As you approach this home you are sure to notice the tremendous curb-appeal, with custom hand-made shutters and picturesque covered porch. Entering through the front, you will be greeted by a generously-sized living room which opens into the expansive dining area. Continuing back, you will pass through the well-maintained kitchen and into the large rear addition. The convenient powder room rounds out the first floor. Traveling up the main staircase, you will find the second floor with two of the three bedrooms and an oversized hall bath, which conveniently houses the laundry suite. Continue up to the third floor and you will find a large, freshly-painted finished space which has been used as a bedroom, but could also serve as a storage area or bonus space. Check out the pristine partial unfinished basement before heading out to the serene backyard setting, which you will find great for entertaining and perfect for kicking your feet up. This area is fenced in for privacy, and is home to an outdoor shed which offers even more storage.  **Roof 2013, **Boiler 2018, **Water Heater 2023!  Showings start the day after Thanksgiving. Schedule your private tour today!  Check out the Zillow 3D tour!
